<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>403 Forbidden</title>

    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px;
        overflow: hidden;
        font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;

        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, #dbeafe 0%, transparent 28%),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #c7d2fe 0%, transparent 25%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc, #eef2ff);

        position: relative;
      }

      body::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: -180px;
        left: -180px;
        width: 420px;
        height: 420px;
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(20px);
      }

      body::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -180px;
        right: -180px;
        width: 420px;
        height: 420px;
        background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(20px);
      }

      .error-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 700px;
        padding: 55px 45px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 36px;

        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);

        box-shadow:
          0 30px 70px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1),
          0 10px 25px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);

        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .error-container::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: -120px;
        right: -120px;
        width: 260px;
        height: 260px;
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08);
        border-radius: 50%;
      }

      .error-badge {
        width: fit-content;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        padding: 10px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #fef2f2;
        color: #dc2626;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        border: 1px solid #fecaca;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .error-code {
        font-size: 8rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 20px;

        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;

        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .error-title {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #111827;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .error-message {
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.9;
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 0 auto 38px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .error-actions {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 16px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 16px 28px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        font-size: 0.96rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        transition: all 0.28s ease;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #3b82f6);
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 35px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 44px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.28);
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        background: white;
        color: #111827;
        border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      }

      .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: #111827;
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .error-container {
          padding: 42px 26px;
          border-radius: 28px;
        }

        .error-code {
          font-size: 5.5rem;
        }

        .error-title {
          font-size: 1.9rem;
        }

        .error-message {
          font-size: 0.96rem;
        }

        .error-actions {
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .btn {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="error-container">
      <div class="error-badge">🚫 Security Verification Failed</div>

      <div class="error-code">403</div>

      <h1 class="error-title">Access Forbidden</h1>

      <p class="error-message">
        Your request could not be completed because the CSRF token is missing,
        invalid, or has expired. Refresh the page and try again to continue
        securely.
      </p>

      <div class="error-actions">
        <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-primary"> Return Home </a>

        <a href="javascript:location.reload();" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Refresh Page
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
